### 🟡 MEDIUM

**5. Eager Test** — `OrderProcessor_FullWorkflow_Succeeds` (line 57)

Calls **7 distinct** production methods: `ValidateOrder`, `CalculateTotal`, `ApplyDiscount`, `ReserveInventory`, `ProcessPayment`, `SendConfirmation`, `UpdateOrderHistory`. A failure could come from any of them. **Fix:** test each method individually; if an end-to-end check is needed, mark it as `[TestCategory("Integration")]` and accept the trade-off.

